{"inkVersion":21,"root":[["\n","\n","\n","\n","\n",{"->":"prologue"},["done",{"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"prologue":["#","^scene:background1","/#","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^My name is Aiden.","\n","^When I was fifteen years old, half of my village died from a disease no one could name.","\n","^And more kept dying, day after day.","\n","^I became a doctor and spent many years searching for a cure.","\n","^Finally, I found a lead.","\n","^But the last ingredients — the Shimmerleaf, the Glaceweed — they have been extinct for two hundred years.","\n","#","^scene:background2","/#","#","^hide_character","/#","^The village witch found me. She said she could send me back.","\n","^Five days. That is all she could give me.","\n","^After that, the window closes. Forever.","\n",{"->":"time_transition"},null],"time_transition":[["#","^time_transition","/#","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^Five days. Two herbs. I need to move fast.","\n","#","^scene:map","/#","#","^speaker:","/#","^There seems to be a village nearby. Someone there might know about the Shimmerleaf.","\n","ev","str","^Head to the village","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["\n",{"->":"day1_arrival"},{"#f":5}]}],null],"day1_arrival":["#","^scene:village_day1","/#","#","^portrait:aiden","/#","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^Three people nearby.","\n",{"->":"village_hub"},null],"village_hub":[["#","^scene:village_hub","/#","#","^portrait:none","/#","#","^speaker:","/#","ev","str","^Talk to Mara — the hunter","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^Talk to Finn — the woodcutter","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},"ev","str","^Talk to Isla — the village elder","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":4},"ev","str","^I have learned enough. Time to head out.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-3","flg":4},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"mara_entry"},"\n",null],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"finn_entry"},"\n",null],"c-2":["^ ",{"->":"isla_entry"},"\n",null],"c-3":["^ ",{"->":"day1_end"},"\n",null]}],null],"mara_entry":["ev",{"VAR?":"talked_to_mara"},"/ev",["du","ev",true,"==","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["pop","\n","#","^portrait:mara","/#","#","^speaker:Mara","/#","^Still here?","\n",{"->":"mara_questions"},{"->":".^.^.^.6"},null]}],["du","ev",false,"==","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["pop","\n","#","^portrait:mara","/#","#","^speaker:Mara","/#","^You are not from here. What do you want?","\n","#","^portrait:aiden","/#","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^My name is Aiden. I am looking for the Shimmerleaf.","\n","#","^portrait:mara","/#","#","^speaker:Mara","/#","^Shimmerleaf. Long way to come for a plant.","\n","#","^portrait:aiden","/#","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^It is important. Do you know it?","\n","#","^portrait:mara","/#","#","^speaker:Mara","/#","^You will need to survive in the forest. Ask me what you need.","\n","ev",true,"/ev",{"VAR=":"talked_to_mara","re":true},{"->":"mara_questions"},{"->":".^.^.^.6"},null]}],"pop","nop","\n",null],"mara_questions":[["ev","str","^How do I choose where to sleep?","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^What do you know about the Shimmerleaf?","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},"ev","str","^Have you seen anyone else pass through?","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":4},"ev","str","^That is all I needed.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-3","flg":4},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"mara_campsite"},"\n",null],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"mara_shimmerleaf"},"\n",null],"c-2":["^ ",{"->":"mara_others"},"\n",null],"c-3":["^ ",{"->":"village_hub"},"\n",null]}],null],"mara_campsite":[["#","^portrait:mara","/#","#","^speaker:Mara","/#","^Ground first. Always ground first.","\n","^Find somewhere high — not a hilltop, just higher than what surrounds it. Water runs downhill. Sleep in a low spot and you wake up wet. Or you do not wake up at all.","\n","^Stay back from water. Fifteen steps at least. The bank looks stable until it is not.","\n","#","^speaker:Mara","/#","^Now tell me — flat ground right beside a stream, or a slight rise thirty steps away. Which do you take?","\n","ev","str","^The flat spot — easier access to water","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^The rise, further from water","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n","#","^portrait:mara","/#","#","^speaker:Mara","/#","^Easy access to water. Easy access to flooding. The rise. Always the rise.","\n",{"->":"mara_questions"},null],"c-1":["\n","#","^portrait:mara","/#","#","^speaker:Mara","/#","^Good. You are thinking like someone who wants to wake up dry.","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"has_dried_berries"},"!","/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","ev",true,"/ev",{"VAR=":"has_dried_berries","re":true},"#","^item:dried_berries","/#","^Here. You will need the energy.","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.14"},null]}],"nop","\n",{"->":"mara_questions"},null]}],null],"mara_shimmerleaf":["#","^portrait:mara","/#","#","^speaker:Mara","/#","^It grows near water but not in it.","\n","^The north-facing edges of the forest, mostly. Less sun. The plant likes the shade.","\n",{"->":"mara_questions"},null],"mara_others":["#","^portrait:mara","/#","#","^speaker:Mara","/#","^Two, last week. One camped by the river bend. Gone before sunrise — tent half-buried in mud by morning.","\n","#","^speaker:Mara","/#","^The other listened. She is probably doing fine out there.","\n","#","^speaker:Mara","/#","^Some people learn from others. Some learn from the mud.","\n",{"->":"mara_questions"},null],"finn_entry":["ev",{"VAR?":"talked_to_finn"},"/ev",["du","ev",true,"==","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["pop","\n","#","^portrait:finn","/#","#","^speaker:Finn","/#","^Back again?","\n",{"->":"finn_questions"},{"->":".^.^.^.6"},null]}],["du","ev",false,"==","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["pop","\n","#","^portrait:finn","/#","#","^speaker:Finn","/#","^You look lost. First time out here?","\n","#","^portrait:aiden","/#","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^I am looking for the Shimmerleaf.","\n","#","^portrait:finn","/#","#","^speaker:Finn","/#","^Then you will need to survive in the forest. Ask away.","\n","ev",true,"/ev",{"VAR=":"talked_to_finn","re":true},{"->":"finn_questions"},{"->":".^.^.^.6"},null]}],"pop","nop","\n",null],"finn_questions":[["ev","str","^Any dangers I should watch for out there?","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^That is all I needed.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"finn_overhead"},"\n",null],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"village_hub"},"\n",null]}],null],"finn_overhead":[["#","^portrait:finn","/#","#","^speaker:Finn","/#","^The trees will kill you before the cold does — trust me. Dead branches. Widowmakers, we call them. Always look up before you pitch your tent. Always.","\n","^And never build fire under a canopy. One spark into dry leaves overhead and it all comes down on you. Open sky above your fire. No exceptions.","\n","#","^speaker:Finn","/#","^Two spots. One under a big oak — sheltered. One in a clearing — open sky but you would feel the wind. Which one?","\n","ev","str","^Under the oak — better shelter","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^The clearing — open sky is safer","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n","#","^portrait:finn","/#","#","^speaker:Finn","/#","^That oak has three dead branches I can see from here. Any one comes down in the night... Always choose the clearing, which is the open area.","\n",{"->":"finn_questions"},null],"c-1":["\n","#","^portrait:finn","/#","#","^speaker:Finn","/#","^Exactly. Wind you can deal with. A branch through your tent you cannot.","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"has_rope"},"!","/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","ev",true,"/ev",{"VAR=":"has_rope","re":true},"#","^item:rope","/#","^Here. It will boost your energy.","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.14"},null]}],"nop","\n",{"->":"finn_questions"},null]}],null],"isla_entry":["ev",{"VAR?":"talked_to_isla"},"/ev",["du","ev",true,"==","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["pop","\n","#","^portrait:isla","/#","#","^speaker:Isla","/#","^You again. Sit, if you like.","\n",{"->":"isla_questions"},{"->":".^.^.^.6"},null]}],["du","ev",false,"==","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["pop","\n","#","^portrait:isla","/#","#","^speaker:Isla","/#","^You have the look of someone who has come a long way.","\n","#","^portrait:aiden","/#","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^I have. I am looking for the Shimmerleaf.","\n","#","^portrait:isla","/#","#","^speaker:Isla","/#","^Then sit for a moment. There are things worth knowing.","\n","ev",true,"/ev",{"VAR=":"talked_to_isla","re":true},{"->":"isla_questions"},{"->":".^.^.^.6"},null]}],"pop","nop","\n",null],"isla_questions":[["ev","str","^What do you know about making camp?","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^What do you know about the Shimmerleaf?","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},"ev","str","^That is all I needed.","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-2","flg":4},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"isla_camp"},"\n",null],"c-1":["^ ",{"->":"isla_shimmerleaf"},"\n",null],"c-2":["^ ",{"->":"village_hub"},"\n",null]}],null],"isla_camp":[["#","^portrait:isla","/#","#","^speaker:Isla","/#","^Wind is the one people forget. They think about rain, they think about cold. Not wind — until it is three in the morning and their fire is ash and their blankets are wet.","\n","^Face your shelter away from the wind. Find something solid at your back. A boulder, a bank, a hill.","\n","^And cold air flows downhill just like water. Hollows fill up with cold before anywhere else. Sleep high. Sleep dry. Sleep warm.","\n","#","^speaker:Isla","/#","^A hollow between two hills — sheltered, soft ground. Or a flat open space on the hillside — exposed, higher up. Where do you sleep?","\n","ev","str","^The hollow — sheltered and quiet","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},"ev","str","^The hillside — higher and better air","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-1","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n","#","^portrait:isla","/#","#","^speaker:Isla","/#","^Cold air pools in hollows like water in a bowl. By midnight shivering. By dawn sick.","\n","^Cold flows downhill — remember that.","\n",{"->":"isla_questions"},null],"c-1":["\n","#","^portrait:isla","/#","#","^speaker:Isla","/#","^You understand. Most people do not until they have spent a night in a hollow.","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"has_water_pouch"},"!","/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","ev",true,"/ev",{"VAR=":"has_water_pouch","re":true},"#","^item:water_pouch","/#","^Take this. Keep it full.","\n",{"->":".^.^.^.14"},null]}],"nop","\n",{"->":"isla_questions"},null]}],null],"isla_shimmerleaf":["#","^portrait:isla","/#","#","^speaker:Isla","/#","^My grandmother collected it. Said the rain wakes something in the leaf. Half an hour after a storm passes, they glow — pale green. Easy to spot. But only for a short while.","\n","^You need to already be there when the rain stops. Camped and waiting.","\n",{"->":"isla_questions"},null],"day1_end":["#","^portrait:aiden","/#","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^I know where to go. I'll head to the north edge of the forest tomorrow.","\n",{"->":"day2_transition"},null],"day2_transition":[["#","^day_advance","/#","#","^scene:village_day1","/#","#","^portrait:aiden","/#","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^It's another day. Half day's walk to the forest. I need to move now.","\n","ev","str","^Head out","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":20},{"c-0":["^ ",{"->":"day2_forest"},"\n",{"#f":5}]}],null],"day2_forest":["#","^scene:path_to_forest","/#","#","^portrait:aiden","/#","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^Rain is coming. I can feel it in the air.","\n","^I need to make camp now — and be ready to search the moment it stops.","\n",{"->":"day2_campsite"},null],"day2_campsite":[["#","^minigame:campsite day:2","/#","ev","str","^Continue","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},null],"g-0":["ev",{"VAR?":"stamina_depleted"},"/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","ev","str","^stamina","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"fail_reason","re":true},{"->":"day2_buffer"},{"->":".^.^.^.4"},null]}],"nop","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"mg_campsite_success"},"/ev",["du","ev",true,"==","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["pop","\n","ev","str","^good","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"campsite_quality","re":true},{"->":"day2_fire_collect"},{"->":".^.^.^.12"},null]}],["du","ev",false,"==","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["pop","\n","ev","str","^poor","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"campsite_quality","re":true},{"->":"day2_fire_collect"},{"->":".^.^.^.12"},null]}],"pop","nop","\n",null]}],null],"day2_fire_collect":[["#","^scene:path_to_forest","/#","#","^portrait:aiden","/#","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^It's becoming colder. I need to gather wood to make fire. Move fast.","\n","#","^minigame:fire_collect day:2","/#","ev","str","^Continue","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},null],"g-0":["ev",{"VAR?":"stamina_depleted"},"/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","ev","str","^fire","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"fail_reason","re":true},{"->":"day2_buffer"},{"->":".^.^.^.4"},null]}],"nop","\n",{"->":"day2_fire"},null]}],null],"day2_fire":[["#","^minigame:fire_campsite day:2","/#","ev","str","^Continue","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},null],"g-0":["ev",{"VAR?":"stamina_depleted"},"/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n","ev","str","^fire","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"fail_reason","re":true},{"->":"day2_buffer"},{"->":".^.^.^.4"},null]}],"nop","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"mg_fire_campsite_success"},"/ev",["du","ev",true,"==","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["pop","\n",{"->":"day2_rain_stops"},{"->":".^.^.^.12"},null]}],["du","ev",false,"==","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["pop","\n","ev","str","^fire","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"fail_reason","re":true},{"->":"day2_buffer"},{"->":".^.^.^.12"},null]}],"pop","nop","\n",null]}],null],"day2_rain_stops":["ev",{"VAR?":"campsite_quality"},"str","^good","/str","==","/ev",[{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["\n",{"->":"day2_search_good"},{"->":".^.^.^.9"},null]}],[{"->":".^.b"},{"b":["\n",{"->":"day2_search_poor"},{"->":".^.^.^.9"},null]}],"nop","\n",null],"day2_search_good":[["#","^scene:forest_dawn_wet","/#","#","^portrait:aiden","/#","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^There — at the edge of the tree line. A pale green glow.","\n","#","^minigame:search day:2 difficulty:easy","/#","ev","str","^Continue","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},null],"g-0":["ev",{"VAR?":"mg_search_success"},"/ev",["du","ev",true,"==","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["pop","\n","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^Shimmerleaf. The rain woke it up. And I was here to see it.","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"herb_count"},1,"+","/ev",{"VAR=":"herb_count","re":true},{"->":"day2_morning_good"},{"->":".^.^.^.6"},null]}],["du","ev",false,"==","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["pop","\n","ev","str","^missed_herb","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"fail_reason","re":true},"#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^I was too slow. The glow faded before I could reach it.","\n",{"->":"day2_buffer"},{"->":".^.^.^.6"},null]}],"pop","nop","\n",null]}],null],"day2_search_poor":[["#","^scene:forest_dawn_wet","/#","#","^portrait:aiden","/#","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^The rain stopped. But this ground — I can barely move without sinking.","\n","^The window is open. I cannot waste it.","\n","#","^minigame:search day:2 difficulty:hard","/#","ev","str","^Continue","/str","/ev",{"*":".^.c-0","flg":4},{"c-0":["\n",{"->":".^.^.g-0"},null],"g-0":["ev",{"VAR?":"mg_search_success"},"/ev",["du","ev",true,"==","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["pop","\n","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^Got it. But this ground nearly cost me everything.","\n","ev",{"VAR?":"herb_count"},1,"+","/ev",{"VAR=":"herb_count","re":true},"ev",4,"/ev",{"VAR=":"next_day_stamina_max","re":true},{"->":"day2_morning_good"},{"->":".^.^.^.6"},null]}],["du","ev",false,"==","/ev",{"->":".^.b","c":true},{"b":["pop","\n","ev","str","^missed_herb","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"fail_reason","re":true},"#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","^I could see the glow — just out of reach. The mud held me back.","\n",{"->":"day2_buffer"},{"->":".^.^.^.6"},null]}],"pop","nop","\n",null]}],null],"day2_morning_good":["#","^scene:forest_morning","/#","#","^portrait:aiden","/#","#","^speaker:Aiden","/#","ev",{"VAR